{"name": "directory-pytree", "metadata": {"name": "directory-pytree", "version": "0.1.0", "classifiers": [], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "A simple directory tree display tool", "upload_time": 1732262256}, "documentation": ["```markdown\r\n# PyTree\r\n\r\n\u4e00\u4e2a\u7b80\u5355\u800c\u5f3a\u5927\u7684\u76ee\u5f55\u6811\u663e\u793a\u5de5\u5177\u3002\r\n\r\n## \u5b89\u88c5\r\n\r\n\u200d\u200d```bash\r\npip install directory-pytree\r\n```\r\n\r\n## \u4f7f\u7528\u65b9\u6cd5\r\n\r\n```bash\r\npytree [\u8def\u5f84] [-e \u6392\u9664\u76ee\u5f55] [-L \u5c42\u7ea7] [-s]\r\n```\r\n\r\n### \u53c2\u6570\u8bf4\u660e\r\n\r\n- \u8def\u5f84: \u8981\u663e\u793a\u7684\u76ee\u5f55\u8def\u5f84\uff08\u53ef\u9009\uff0c\u9ed8\u8ba4\u4e3a\u5f53\u524d\u76ee\u5f55\uff09\r\n- -e, --exclude: \u8981\u6392\u9664\u7684\u76ee\u5f55\u5217\u8868\r\n- -L, --level: \u6700\u5927\u663e\u793a\u6df1\u5ea6\r\n- -s, --size: \u663e\u793a\u6587\u4ef6\u5927\u5c0f\r\n\r\n### \u793a\u4f8b\r\n\r\n```bash\r\npytree\r\npytree /path/to/directory\r\npytree -s -L 2\r\npytree -e node_modules .git\r\n```\r\n\r\n## \u5f00\u53d1\r\n\r\n1. \u514b\u9686\u4ed3\u5e93\r\n2. \u5b89\u88c5\u5f00\u53d1\u4f9d\u8d56: pip install -e \".[dev]\"\r\n3. \u8fd0\u884c\u6d4b\u8bd5: pytest\r\n\r\n## \u8bb8\u53ef\u8bc1\r\n\r\nMIT License\r\nCopyright (c) 2023 Chen Ding Gang\r\n"], "modules": [{"name": "pytree.main", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "pytree.main.print_tree", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "directory", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "exclude_dirs", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "prefix", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "level", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "max_level", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "show_size", "type": null, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["\u6253\u5370\u76ee\u5f55\u6811\u7ed3\u6784"]}, {"name": "pytree.main.format_size", "asynchronous": false,